page.title: 18HOME LIFE
page.content: In the morning I woke up at 800am I then brushed my teeth and got changed and ate my breakfast .Then I went to school in my mams car then I saw a film and later talked about it.After first playtime I worked I did some maths about circumference and diameter then dinner time came.For dinner I had tomato,peas,fish and cheese scones after that we had pudding which was biscuits with cream and a cherry on the biscuit.After dinner and last playtime I had to work.For the work I did some maths with a story which was about sets also I did some topic about the human body then at half past three which was home time I walked home with one of my brothers.At about half past four one of my friends called for me.He was in my brothers class. {(continued on page 19) {
